      "content": "The weariness you feel is deeply understandable when you've been struggling for so long, and exhaustion is a very real feeling. However, the desire to stop the pain doesn't automatically mean that ending your life is the only logical way to find peace. There are skilled professionals who can help you find gentle ways to relieve the pressure and emptiness you are carrying. Please give them a chance to show you if there are other paths to peace.",
